  title: 'Overview',
  paragraphs: [
    'Dermal fillers made with hyaluronic acid can restore support and refine contour with a harmony-first approach. At D-Essence, we prioritize structure before volume to maintain balance and natural proportions.',
    'Product selection (rheology/firmness) is tailored per area—cheeks, lips, chin, jawline—so results integrate seamlessly with your features while respecting tissue quality.'
  ],
  indicationsTitle: 'Indications',
  indications: [
    'Midface support (cheeks) & lift',
    'Lip definition & hydration',
    'Nasolabial / marionette softening',
    'Chin projection & jawline contour',
